headline.print_headline: Ukraine Agreement Built on Fragile Foundations
headline.main: Ukraine Agreement Built on Fragile Foundations

lead_paragraph: The agreement designed to pull Ukraine back from the brink of civil war had been floundering around lunchtime on Thursday, so U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry and Russia's Sergei Lavrov, a smoker, stepped outside for a private word in the open air.
